text: Irina Skripnik (born 26 January 1970) is a Belarusian cross-country skier. She competed at the 1998 Winter Olympics and the 2002 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1970 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian female cross-country skiers Category:Olympic cross-country skiers of Belarus Category:Cross-country skiers at the 1998 Winter Olympics Category:Cross- country skiers at the 2002 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tula, Russia
